          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Small Employer Retirement Savings Auto-Enrollment Credit Act </b></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow a three-year $500 business-related tax credit for eligible small employers who include and maintain an automatic contribution arrangement in an employer-sponsored retirement plan. </p> <p>An &quot;eligible employer&quot; is an employer with no more than 100 employees who received at least $5,000 of compensation from the employer for the preceding year. </p>]]></text>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <updateDate>2017-10-02T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2017-10-04T14:27:45Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        </item>
